query:
select to_jsonb(bookmarks.*) as item
            from bookmarks
            where bookmarks.title ilike '%' || $1 || '%'
            and bookmarks.ap_user_id = $2
            union
            select to_jsonb(lists.*) as item
            from lists
            where lists.title ilike '%' || $1 || '%'
            and lists.ap_user_id = $2
            limit 10
